      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Sharon.—The well-known plain of this name lay west of Jordan, between Carmel and Joppa, along the coast of the Great Sea. The old conjecture that Shirion, i.e., mount Hermon (Deuteronomy 3:9; Psalm 29:6) should be read, is probably right.",
